{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dea7e9b09b","title":"为朱光题词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fedb71ffbd","index":0,"year":1949,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"dea7e9b09b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"74be3e8513","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dea7e9b09b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1949年8月，朱光奉命南下广州，参加广州的接管工作。朱光离开东北，进关南下途经北平时，来到中南海。朱德应朱光之请，即席书写了一《赠友人》诗相赠。尔后，朱光又应毛泽东之请，到其书房叙谈，毛泽东亲笔为朱光题词一幅。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b348af0889","type":"title","text":"为朱光题词口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dea7e9b09b"},{"id":"74be3e8513","type":"paragraph","text":"到南方去，同原在南方工作的同志团结在一起，将南方工作做好，这是我的希望。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dea7e9b09b"},{"id":"3a5954d6ba","type":"paragraph","text":"朱光同志","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dea7e9b09b"},{"id":"6f26c43e83","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dea7e9b09b"}],"page":{"id":"091a4a375d","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dea7e9b09b","start":119,"end":119}}}},"__N_SSG":true}